          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「へえ、君も夷の生まれか。言葉の端々に懐かしい訛りがあるね」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "都の流行りなど、我ら夷には到底理解できぬ別世界の出来事だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「おい、あっちの夷が道を尋ねているぞ。誰か言葉のわかる奴はいないか」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "brutish, unsophisticated warrior (esp. used by Kyoto samurai to refer to samurai from eastern Japan)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「荒夷どもめ、無作法に御所へ踏み込むとは許し難い！」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "武勇だけが自慢の夷が、宮中の儀礼をこなせるとは到底思えぬ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「おのれ、都の連中に夷と蔑まれたままではいられぬ。戦で力を見せつけてやろう」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "foreigner",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「南蛮から来た夷は、我らとは全く異なる神を信じているそうだ」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "黒船に乗って現れた夷の姿に、役人たちは対応に苦慮していた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「見て、あそこの夷が持っている道具、キラキラ光って不思議だね」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
